            <div id="myTabContent" class="tab-content">

                <div class="tab-pane fade in active" id="allgender">
                    <div class="sponsor-content-aria wow fadeInDown" data-wow-delay=".4s">
                        <p>Every child deserves a happy & prosperous life.Irrespective of economic status, every
                            children has the right to education.But to many children right here in our country aren't
                            getting the opportunity to reach their full potential .many children are not getting
                            education not because they are unwilling but because their families cannot afford their
                            books, uniforms and academic fee.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="sponsor-slider-section wow fadeInDown" data-wow-delay=".4s">
                        <div id="demo">
                            <div class="row">
                                <div class="span12">

